The '''adrenal gland''' was a gland on many lifeforms. [[Yuuzhan Vong]] coral had one, from which [[Sinsor Khal]] extracted tissue for analysis and discovered that its genetic sequences translated to all of the organism's cells enabling it to spawn and communicate with other cells.

